💡 What skills will be needed in the future? How can we best meet the aspirations and challenges of the twin green and digital transition during an energy crisis, while tackling climate change? These are burning issues that will be reflected on during the BIBBK22 Congress.

📢 Join the conversation on #digitalisation, #sustainability and other key trends for future skills at the #BIBBK22 event, 🗓️ 27-28 October, under the theme "Future Skills–Thinking About Progress" to be held at the World Conference Center, Bonn 🇩🇪.

It covers:
✅ reinforced Youth Guarantee
✅ future-proof vocational training
✅ quality apprenticeships
✅ other measures
